Package: log-guardian
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ipset, libbpf1, libcurl4, libpcre2-8-0, libsqlite3-0, libssl3, libelf1, libz1, liburing2, adduser
Recommends: nginx, iptables | nftables
Maintainer: Linux Log Guardian <community@log-guardian.local>
Description: Linux Log Guardian — nginx log WAF and kernel ban
 Core: nginx access log ingest, WAF rules, OpenAPI schema firewall,
 automatic ipset ban pipeline. Includes log-guardian analyzer and
 log-guardian-daemon (eBPF/XDP optional).
